### BlockTask API Tests
### VS Code: Install REST Client extension to use this file

### ============= AUTHENTICATION =============

### Register a new user (Client)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/users/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testclient",
  "email": "client@test.com",
  "password": "TestPass123!",
  "password_confirm": "TestPass123!",
  "first_name": "Test",
  "last_name": "Client",
  "user_type": "client",
  "phone_number": "+2250102030405"
}

### Register a new user (Provider)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/users/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testprovider",
  "email": "provider@test.com",
  "password": "TestPass123!",
  "password_confirm": "TestPass123!",
  "first_name": "Test",
  "last_name": "Provider",
  "user_type": "provider",
  "phone_number": "+2250506070809"
}

### Login (JWT Token)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/token/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "client@test.com",
  "password": "TestPass123!"
}

### Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/token/refresh/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh": "eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..."
}

### ============= USERS =============

### Get Current User Profile
GET http://localhost:8000/api/users/me/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Profile
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/users/me/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "first_name": "Updated",
  "phone_number": "+2251112131415"
}

### ============= CATEGORIES =============

### List All Categories
GET http://localhost:8000/api/categories/

### Get Category Detail
GET http://localhost:8000/api/categories/livraison/

### ============= MISSIONS =============

### List All Missions (with filters)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/missions/?status=open&ordering=-created_at

### Get Available Missions (for providers)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/missions/available/
Authorization: Bearer {{provider_token}}

### Get My Missions (as client)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/missions/my_missions/
Authorization: Bearer {{client_token}}

### Create New Mission
POST http://localhost:8000/api/missions/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_token}}

{
  "title": "Livraison colis urgent",
  "description": "Livraison d'un colis important avant 18h",
  "category": 1,
  "pickup_address": "Cocody, Abidjan",
  "pickup_latitude": 5.3520,
  "pickup_longitude": -4.0083,
  "delivery_address": "Plateau, Abidjan",
  "delivery_latitude": 5.3206,
  "delivery_longitude": -4.0161,
  "pickup_contact_name": "Amadou",
  "pickup_contact_phone": "+2250102030405",
  "delivery_contact_name": "Fatou",
  "delivery_contact_phone": "+2250506070809",
  "budget": 50.00,
  "currency": "USDT",
  "deadline": "2026-06-12T18:00:00Z",
  "estimated_duration": 60,
  "requires_vehicle": true,
  "requires_photo": true,
  "requires_signature": true
}

### Get Mission Detail
GET http://localhost:8000/api/missions/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Apply to Mission (as provider)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/missions/1/apply/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{provider_token}}

{
  "proposed_price": 45.00,
  "estimated_duration": 45,
  "cover_message": "Je peux réaliser cette mission rapidement avec mon scooter",
  "proposed_deadline": "2026-06-12T17:30:00Z"
}

### Accept Application (as client)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/missions/1/accept_application/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_token}}

{
  "application_id": 1
}

### Start Mission (as provider)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/missions/1/start/
Authorization: Bearer {{provider_token}}

### Submit Proof (as provider)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/missions/1/submit_proof/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{provider_token}}

{
  "proofs": [
    {
      "type": "photo",
      "url": "https://storage.blocktask.io/proofs/photo1.jpg",
      "location": "5.3206,-4.0161"
    }
  ]
}

### Validate Mission (as client)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/missions/1/validate/
Authorization: Bearer {{client_token}}

### Complete Mission
POST http://localhost:8000/api/missions/1/complete/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel Mission
POST http://localhost:8000/api/missions/1/cancel/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_token}}

{
  "reason": "Mission annulée - changement de plans"
}

### Open Dispute
POST http://localhost:8000/api/missions/1/dispute/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{client_token}}

{
  "reason": "MISSION_NOT_COMPLETED",
  "description": "Le prestataire n'a pas complété la mission correctement"
}

### Get Mission Applications (as client)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/missions/1/applications/
Authorization: Bearer {{client_token}}

### Get Mission Stats
GET http://localhost:8000/api/missions/stats/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============= APPLICATIONS =============

### List My Applications (as provider)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/applications/my_applications/
Authorization: Bearer {{provider_token}}

### Withdraw Application
POST http://localhost:8000/api/applications/1/withdraw/
Authorization: Bearer {{provider_token}}

### ============= BOOKMARKS =============

### Toggle Bookmark
POST http://localhost:8000/api/bookmarks/toggle/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "mission_id": 1,
  "notes": "Mission intéressante pour demain",
  "alert_enabled": true
}

### List Bookmarks
GET http://localhost:8000/api/bookmarks/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============= ADMIN =============

### Django Admin
GET http://localhost:8000/admin/

### API Schema
GET http://localhost:8000/api/schema/

### ============= TEST WORKFLOW =============
# 1. Register client and provider
# 2. Login as client and create mission
# 3. Login as provider and apply
# 4. Client accepts application
# 5. Provider starts mission
# 6. Provider submits proof
# 7. Client validates mission
# 8. Payment released via blockchain
